1
00:01:03,620 --> 00:01:05,910
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,160 --> 00:01:09,840
[Episode 5]

3
00:01:11,030 --> 00:01:14,470
General's Mansion

4
00:01:16,230 --> 00:01:17,200
What's with the knocking?

5
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:17,950
Get in here!

6
00:01:20,590 --> 00:01:22,150
General, the palace
has just issued an edict.

7
00:01:22,150 --> 00:01:24,350
The empress dowager has moved up
your wedding to Miss Jiang.

8
00:01:24,350 --> 00:01:24,920
Really?

9
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:26,280
General.

10
00:01:27,070 --> 00:01:28,400
General.

11
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:29,840
It's absolutely true.

12
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:30,760
General!

13
00:01:33,070 --> 00:01:35,930
-General, where are you going?
-Aunt loves me more.

14
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:38,000
Come with me to the treasury
to select some fine items.

15
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:40,150
Tomorrow I'll go discuss
the wedding arrangements.

16
00:01:40,150 --> 00:01:40,789
Yes.

17
00:01:40,789 --> 00:01:43,430
-Don't go, General.
-Don't leave us, General.

18
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:46,150
The usual.

19
00:01:46,509 --> 00:01:47,560
Take care of them.

20
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,120
Yes.

21
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:50,280
-General.
-General. General.

22
00:01:55,970 --> 00:01:58,880
[Grand Tutor's Mansion]

23
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,910
Imperial Garden?

24
00:02:32,470 --> 00:02:34,120
How could Mother be here?

25
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:36,750
My Lady, General Xun is here.

26
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,190
Tell him I'm feeling unwell

27
00:02:39,190 --> 00:02:40,250
and cannot see him.

28
00:02:40,470 --> 00:02:42,190
He's not here to see you.

29
00:02:42,190 --> 00:02:44,030
The empress dowager
has moved up the wedding date.

30
00:02:44,030 --> 00:02:46,750
H-He's here to discuss the arrangements.

31
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,310
What?

32
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:53,630
General Xun, you're too kind.

33
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,240
We'll be family soon.

34
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,590
There's no need to spend so much.

35
00:02:56,590 --> 00:02:57,870
Since my aunt has granted this marriage,

36
00:02:57,870 --> 00:02:59,560
it's a royal blessing.

37
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:01,190
We must treat it with proper respect.

38
00:03:01,190 --> 00:03:03,050
Father-in-law, please don't...

39
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,880
Calling you father-in-law now,

40
00:03:06,030 --> 00:03:07,190
is it a bit premature?

41
00:03:07,190 --> 00:03:08,960
Not at all. The timing is perfect.

42
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:10,630
General, you really have excellent taste.

43
00:03:10,630 --> 00:03:12,840
These are all first-class treasures.

44
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:15,560
I came today to discuss
the wedding arrangements.

45
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:18,190
Do you have any other requests?

46
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,590
General, being able to form
a family bond with you

47
00:03:21,590 --> 00:03:23,800
is a blessing we've earned
from several lifetimes.

48
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:25,470
How could we have any requests?

49
00:03:25,470 --> 00:03:26,190
Well, about Li...

50
00:03:26,190 --> 00:03:28,470
A daughter, once married,
belongs to her husband's family.

51
00:03:28,470 --> 00:03:29,280
In the future,

52
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:31,740
we'll be counting
on your support, General.

53
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:34,630
What are you all doing here?

54
00:03:34,750 --> 00:03:36,000
You came just in time.

55
00:03:36,190 --> 00:03:37,000
Li,

56
00:03:37,310 --> 00:03:39,960
why didn't you return to my mansion
after leaving the palace?

57
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:42,020
I've been waiting for you for so long.

58
00:03:42,030 --> 00:03:43,150
The empress dowager said

59
00:03:43,150 --> 00:03:44,800
men and women should keep their distance,

60
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:47,060
so we shouldn't meet before our wedding.

61
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,400
General,

62
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,200
please leave.

63
00:03:58,030 --> 00:03:58,590
Well...

64
00:03:58,910 --> 00:04:01,430
Don't worry about my aunt.

65
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:02,960
You just need to

66
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,800
be obedient

67
00:04:04,910 --> 00:04:06,680
and keep me happy.

68
00:04:12,870 --> 00:04:13,630
Fine.

69
00:04:15,190 --> 00:04:17,589
But the conditions we agreed upon earlier,

70
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:20,899
you haven't forgotten them,
have you, General?

71
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,070
Li,

72
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:25,160
do you really think

73
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:27,090
I don't know what you're thinking?

74
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,680
My patience is limited.

75
00:04:30,950 --> 00:04:31,720
Be good.

76
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:34,720
Come back to
the General's Mansion with me now.

77
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,390
I won't go.

78
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,560
General, please calm down.

79
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:40,360
Li, apologize quickly.

80
00:04:40,950 --> 00:04:43,360
It's all our fault.
Your father and I have spoiled you.

81
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,720
The General treats you so well,

82
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:46,630
yet you show no gratitude
and defy him to his face.

83
00:04:46,630 --> 00:04:48,290
What kind of behavior is this?

84
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,430
You want to use me

85
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:58,650
to exchange for wealth and status.

86
00:05:00,630 --> 00:05:02,240
What a foolish dream.

87
00:05:04,630 --> 00:05:07,390
I'd rather die.

88
00:05:09,190 --> 00:05:10,310
This marriage—

89
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:13,120
I refuse it!

90
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,920
You dare refuse?

91
00:05:15,310 --> 00:05:16,070
Guards!

92
00:05:19,750 --> 00:05:20,480
My Lady.

93
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,360
Xi'er.

94
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:21,830
You...

95
00:05:22,750 --> 00:05:23,560
What are you doing?

96
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:25,310
Since you don't value your life,

97
00:05:25,310 --> 00:05:27,510
there's no use keeping
this maid alive either.

98
00:05:27,510 --> 00:05:29,000
Let's just kill her and be done with it.

99
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:29,860
Don't you dare!

100
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:32,000
My Lady, I'm not afraid to die.

101
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:34,040
Please don't let them intimidate you.

102
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:34,840
Take her away!

103
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,159
My Lady!

104
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:38,720
Xi'er.

105
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:39,560
My Lady.

106
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,510
Shameless.

107
00:05:50,159 --> 00:05:51,120
Li.

108
00:05:51,830 --> 00:05:53,070
Do you think

109
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:55,800
it'll end with just one maid's death?

110
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:57,310
The empress dowager
arranged this marriage,

111
00:05:57,310 --> 00:05:58,870
and if you just die,

112
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,630
that would be defying the imperial order,

113
00:06:00,630 --> 00:06:03,310
a crime punishable by executing
nine generations of your family.

114
00:06:03,310 --> 00:06:05,480
Grand Tutor Jiang, Ms. Song,

115
00:06:05,630 --> 00:06:08,270
and all the maids and servants
in this household—

116
00:06:08,270 --> 00:06:09,750
none of them would escape.

117
00:06:09,950 --> 00:06:13,350
I will request imperial permission
to oversee the execution

118
00:06:13,750 --> 00:06:17,600
and watch as their heads fall one by one.

119
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:22,190
General Xun, please calm down.

120
00:06:22,190 --> 00:06:24,510
We would be honored to have
a marriage alliance with the Xun family.

121
00:06:24,510 --> 00:06:25,640
You really can't...

122
00:06:26,070 --> 00:06:28,120
Master, please say something!

123
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:29,190
Li.

124
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:32,390
Do you really want to drag down
dozens of family members

125
00:06:32,390 --> 00:06:34,120
to their deaths along with you?

126
00:06:50,630 --> 00:06:52,190
I don't want to force you.

127
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:55,870
I'll give you 3 days to think it over.

128
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,160
General.

129
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,560
-General.
-General Xun.

130
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,840
What should we do now?

131
00:07:04,190 --> 00:07:04,870
General Xun!

132
00:07:04,870 --> 00:07:05,390
General Xun.

133
00:07:05,390 --> 00:07:06,360
General Xun.

134
00:07:06,630 --> 00:07:09,430
-We can talk about it.
-We’ll find a way.

135
00:07:11,770 --> 00:07:15,590
[Wenxiang Pavilion]

136
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:25,360
♪ My thoughts are in turmoil ♪

137
00:07:39,000 --> 00:08:00,560
♪ My heart consumed by unbidden longing ♪

138
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,680
♪ Father, may I ask you ♪

139
00:08:11,810 --> 00:08:12,120
[One year ago]

140
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:14,830
♪ These two treasured robes ♪

141
00:08:14,830 --> 00:08:18,870
♪ From where did they come? ♪

142
00:08:18,870 --> 00:08:23,000
♪ They were bestowed
upon me by His Majesty ♪

143
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:27,190
♪ And why would His Majesty
grant them to you? ♪

144
00:08:27,190 --> 00:08:29,830
♪ To mark the bond
between ruler and subject ♪

145
00:08:29,830 --> 00:08:30,630
♪ His Majesty ♪

146
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:36,320
♪ So even His Majesty honors such bonds ♪

147
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:39,789
♪ Then tell me, Father ♪

148
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:45,510
♪ Have you no bond left with your child? ♪

149
00:08:45,510 --> 00:08:46,150
Bravo!

150
00:08:46,630 --> 00:08:48,270
Bravo!

151
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,600
Young Master, do you think

152
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:58,630
this father and daughter
are too confrontational

153
00:08:58,630 --> 00:08:59,960
and improper?

154
00:09:02,510 --> 00:09:04,200
I merely admire

155
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:09,030
how this woman in the play
defies her parents for love.

156
00:09:09,150 --> 00:09:11,550
She truly is a remarkable woman.

157
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:15,630
I just sigh that life is not like theater.

158
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:17,870
To truly stand against one's family

159
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,120
is no easy matter.

160
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,510
I don't see it that way.

161
00:09:21,030 --> 00:09:22,510
This woman in the play

162
00:09:22,510 --> 00:09:24,870
isn't just fighting for her beloved man,

163
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:28,240
but more for her freedom.

164
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:30,000
Living for yourself

165
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:33,960
is what makes life worth living.

166
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,680
Hurry! Hurry up!

167
00:09:36,750 --> 00:09:37,680
Search quickly!

168
00:09:37,910 --> 00:09:38,600
-Yes.
-Yes.

169
00:09:40,910 --> 00:09:41,870
Turn around!

170
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:43,630
May I borrow your mask, Young Master?

171
00:09:43,630 --> 00:09:44,860
I'll repay you later.

172
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,720
If we don't bring the young lady back,

173
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:48,080
we'll all be in trouble today.

174
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:49,010
Search quickly!

175
00:09:49,150 --> 00:09:49,810
-Yes!
-Yes!

176
00:09:51,390 --> 00:09:51,910
You!

177
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,120
Put it on.

178
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,800
Come here, let me see.

179
00:09:55,550 --> 00:09:56,880
Come here and let me see.

180
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:58,030
Don't block the way.

181
00:09:58,030 --> 00:09:58,760
Turn around.

182
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:00,960
Make way!

183
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:03,660
I'm talking to you.

184
00:10:04,630 --> 00:10:05,550
Young lady.

185
00:10:08,790 --> 00:10:10,720
My wife and I are watching the play.

186
00:10:10,750 --> 00:10:12,200
What business do you have here?

187
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,000
That's right.

188
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,080
You're disturbing our viewing.

189
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:15,200
Please leave quickly.

190
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:16,010
Yes.

191
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,240
Go away now.

192
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:17,960
Indeed.

193
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,510
Let's go check the back.

194
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:36,030
Thank you for saving me, Young Master.

195
00:10:36,030 --> 00:10:37,670
May I know your name?

196
00:10:37,870 --> 00:10:39,030
Call me Zhao.

197
00:10:39,510 --> 00:10:40,510
I am Li.

198
00:10:40,630 --> 00:10:43,080
In three days, I invite you to drink here.

199
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,240
It's a promise.

200
00:10:59,000 --> 00:10:59,910
Waiter!

201
00:11:01,870 --> 00:11:02,750
Waiter!

202
00:11:12,550 --> 00:11:14,080
Why did the opera stop?

203
00:12:11,510 --> 00:12:12,790
Zhao.

204
00:12:25,510 --> 00:12:27,440
I must be dreaming.

205
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,720
Whether in dreams or reality,

206
00:12:46,550 --> 00:12:48,440
I will always be your Zhao.
